{"tid":911050,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛會員 黃巢 又名9527","createTime":"2018-11-21T15:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T13:16:56.000Z","uid":42188,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c35126025e506c78c194f1a71f8f9475afb204","tid":911050,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/132649_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F132649_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5c5cced4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於原post內容過於對<span style=\"color: red;\">黃巢(~9527)陳育權</span>不利比admin搬去站務台，現開個新post整合有關資料<br />\n<br />\nand已向admin舉報及cap圖<br />\n<br />\n原post精彩時空門<br />\n踢爆會員黃巢及9527~真身有埋圖及多位連登巴打認證後發窮惡區3<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/612756/page/2?ref=web&amp;post=31\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/612756/page/2?ref=web&amp;post=31</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>黃巢係9527~同時又係白卡陳育權老母叫愛姐<br />\n<br />\n比一眾連登巴打連續踢爆，所以發窮惡洗板阻人討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已舉報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓會貼cap圖多位巴打仗儀篤爆呢隻白卡五毛<br />\n<br />\n一樓有佢同佢阿媽副尊容，仲有多謝蔣仔提供<br />\n<br />\n二樓會貼cap圖多位巴打仗儀篤爆呢隻白卡五毛<br />\n<br />\n三樓有罪證，去到台灣都有人知<br />\n<br />\n四樓打後係發窮洗板討論總集，唔止我d post連其他無辜會員d post都搞貼金剛棒阻人討論，同濕仔一樣，今日洗左15個post，截之今日為止總數係65個 post<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/011850_cd2b8e352a852ddf1e0942e076a0767b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F011850_cd2b8e352a852ddf1e0942e076a0767b.png&h=e21bb43e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/011851_8e2065722c02f57a2e31a859c72b952f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F011851_8e2065722c02f57a2e31a859c72b952f.png&h=9b9a248a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/011852_0ace8ba150b34433818fe49ec954a385.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F011852_0ace8ba150b34433818fe49ec954a385.png&h=1436daef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/011853_5b6048fd0eb0b2f87b480790c0c41ab1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F011853_5b6048fd0eb0b2f87b480790c0c41ab1.png&h=05d6f083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/132657_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F132657_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=cdffbf33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/132720_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F132720_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ae572264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/132733_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F132733_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ec271128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/132752_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F132752_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7447976f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/132903_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2F